  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras/a5e75a4de17444f6e9f4c9e77d1496d2.avif?t=1759200287\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras_big/a5e75a4de17444f6e9f4c9e77d1496d2.avif?t=1759200287 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dancing fox shrine maiden! A slightly sexy Apparition Find game</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is very simple!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First, watch the dance performed by the Fox Shrine Maiden carefully and memorize it well. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be sure not to get distracted by her sexy allure and miss any part of the dance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to Play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To return to your original world, you must witness all the rituals performed by the Fox Shrine Maiden.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes, apparitions called “Mononoke” will try to deceive you by taking on a form very similar to the Fox Shrine Maiden and tempt you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay strong, watch the rituals carefully, and don’t get enchanted by the seductive fox dance, so you can spot the “mononoke”!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>One! If you believe it is my real self, call upon my name!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Two! If you think it to be an impostor, see through the deception at once!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Know that if you err in either, the ritual fails immediately!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras/9d1df84054821c6568149ea52ca4348c.poster.avif?t=1759200287\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras/9d1df84054821c6568149ea52ca4348c.webm?t=1759200287\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras/9d1df84054821c6568149ea52ca4348c.mp4?t=1759200287\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If your accusation is correct, the 'Mononoke' will be banished, and the lantern will light up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Light all 8 lanterns to return to the world you came from!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Apparition Encyclopedia</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The various forms of the “Mononoke” you have exposed can be recorded in an encyclopedia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Repeat the rituals and create your very own captivating “Apparition Encyclopedia”!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras/818f49fb42b46fdc179c56d47ae450aa.avif?t=1759200287\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras_big/818f49fb42b46fdc179c56d47ae450aa.avif?t=1759200287 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >＜Cast＞</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Fox Shrine Maiden(CV:Maaya Uchida)</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras/a5e75a4de17444f6e9f4c9e77d1496d2.avif?t=1759200287\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras_big/a5e75a4de17444f6e9f4c9e77d1496d2.avif?t=1759200287 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dancing fox shrine maiden! A slightly sexy Apparition Find game</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is very simple!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First, watch the dance performed by the Fox Shrine Maiden carefully and memorize it well. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be sure not to get distracted by her sexy allure and miss any part of the dance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to Play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To return to your original world, you must witness all the rituals performed by the Fox Shrine Maiden.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes, apparitions called “Mononoke” will try to deceive you by taking on a form very similar to the Fox Shrine Maiden and tempt you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay strong, watch the rituals carefully, and don’t get enchanted by the seductive fox dance, so you can spot the “mononoke”!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>One! If you believe it is my real self, call upon my name!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Two! If you think it to be an impostor, see through the deception at once!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Know that if you err in either, the ritual fails immediately!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras/9d1df84054821c6568149ea52ca4348c.poster.avif?t=1759200287\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras/9d1df84054821c6568149ea52ca4348c.webm?t=1759200287\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras/9d1df84054821c6568149ea52ca4348c.mp4?t=1759200287\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If your accusation is correct, the 'Mononoke' will be banished, and the lantern will light up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Light all 8 lanterns to return to the world you came from!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Apparition Encyclopedia</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The various forms of the “Mononoke” you have exposed can be recorded in an encyclopedia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Repeat the rituals and create your very own captivating “Apparition Encyclopedia”!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras/818f49fb42b46fdc179c56d47ae450aa.avif?t=1759200287\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras_big/818f49fb42b46fdc179c56d47ae450aa.avif?t=1759200287 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >＜Cast＞</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Fox Shrine Maiden(CV:Maaya Uchida)</p>",
